description: This file implements two functions related to an HTTP proxy component: 'HttpSpoSbcRequestHeaders' and 'HttpSpoSbcRequestBody', which control the proxy's behavior when handling request headers and body. Both functions currently return a constant indicating relay mode and do not process the input parameters.

methods.name: ULONG HttpSpoSbcRequestHeaders(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession,ANSC_HANDLE hMessage)
methods.description: Handles the request headers in the HTTP simple proxy, currently returning relay mode.

methods.name: ULONG HttpSpoSbcRequestBody(ANSC_HANDLE hThisObject,ANSC_HANDLE hSession,ANSC_HANDLE hMessage)
methods.description: Handles the request body in the HTTP simple proxy, currently returning relay mode.
